cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|I play new suits by responder, be it to an opening bid or overcall, are forcing. However, some experts do not. They play the only forcing bid is a cue bid. I don't like that for 2 reasons:
^Ca) you then give up the cue bid as showing a limit raise or better;
^Cb) you get the bidding pretty high before you can show any suits you have.|
