^-|HT|d|CP||FP||cp|1|AT|^*BMM: ^*N|cp||at|Understanding the Unusual Notrump (UNT) and Michaels Cuebids is easy. However, remembering the differences at the bridge table is a struggle for me. More importantly knowing when a NT is not Unusual or a Cuebid is not Michaels get complicated though that knowledge is very critical. This tutorial is designed to lessen my struggle. You also may find it useful. |
